 transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Simply click the link below to be redirected to our website:</em></p><p><em style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;</em><a href="https://competitiverelocation.com/delivery-services/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(53, 76, 151);"><strong><em>https://competitiverelocation.com</em></strong></a></p><p><em style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;</em></p><p><em style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">We would love the opportunity to assist you with your moving needs. Please feel free to reach out—we look forward to hearing from you soon!</em></p><p><em style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;</em></p><p><em style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">All as well,</em></p><p><em style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Sales Representative&nbsp;</em></p><p><em style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">+1 848-359-8030</em></p><p><em style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Moving and Delivery Specialist</em></p><p><a href="https://competitiverelocation.com" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><em>Competitive Relocation Service</em></a></p><p><br></p><p><em style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">www.competitiverelocation.com</em></p><p><em style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">13 Galaxy Ct, Sewell, New Jersey 08080</em></p><p><em style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">DOT #: 1877921</em></p><p><em style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">MC #: 677599</em></p><p><br></p>', 'TEMPLATE EMAIL  FOR FURNITURE STORE', '2025-05-03 05:38:14', '2025-05-03 05:38:14'),
	(18, 'CONFIRMING of SERVICE  FOR THE CUSTOMER', 'Confirming your ( kind of  Service ) | Competitive Relocation Service', '<p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Hi ( Customer),&nbsp;</strong></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;</strong></p><p><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">I hope this message finds you well.</span></p><p><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">I’m writing to confirm your scheduled delivery on</span><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">[day and date of delivery]. </strong><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Additionally,</span><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> </strong><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">I have sent your invoice via email for your payment with Competitive Relocation Service</span><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">.&nbsp;</strong></p><p><br></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">If you have any questions or need further assistance, please don’t hesitate to contact us at 877-385-2919 or 848-359-8030.</strong></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;</strong></p><p><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Thank you for choosing our service!</span></p><p><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">We are happy to serve you.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Sales Representative&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">+1 848-359-803</span></p><p><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Moving and Delivery Specialist</span></p><p><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Competitive Relocation Service</span></p>', 'CONFIRMING of SERVICE  FOR THE CUSTOMER', '2025-05-03 05:39:38', '2025-05-03 07:12:54'),
	(19, 'THANK YOU LETTER FOR CUSTOMER AFTER THE SERVICE :', 'We Receive your Payment | Competitive Relocation Service', '<p><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Hi ( Customer ),&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">We hope this message finds you well.</span></p><p><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">We are writing to confirm that we have received your payment of</span><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> [amount of service for the job]</strong><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> for the upcoming</span><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> [kind of service]</strong><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> scheduled for</span><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> [day,date for the service]</strong><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">. </span><em style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Our manager will be calling from </em><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><em>5:00 to 8:30 pm today to confirm the time of delivery for tomorrow\'s [kind of service]</em>.</strong></p><p><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Thank you for choosing</span><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> Competitive Relocation Service</strong><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">. We truly appreciate your business and hope to continue assisting you with any future delivery, furniture removal, or moving service needs.</span></p><p><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;</span></p><p><em style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">We look forward to providing a smooth and successful&nbsp; experience with you.</em></p><p><em style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;</em></p><p><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Thank you,</span></p><p><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Sales Representative</span></p><p><br></p><p><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">+1 848-359-8030</span></p><p><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Moving and Delivery Specialist</span></p><p><a href="https://competitiverelocation.com/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(17, 85, 204);">Competitive Relocation Service</a></p><p><br></p>', 'THANK YOU LETTER FOR CUSTOMER AFTER THE SERVICE :', '2025-05-03 05:40:12', '2025-05-03 05:40:12'),
	(20, 'REACHING BACK TO THE CUSTOMER:', 'Are you all set For your Move? | Competitive Relocation Service', '<p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><em>Hi </em>{firstname} {lastname}</strong></p><p><br></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><em>&nbsp;</em></strong></p><p><em style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">I hope you\'re doing well today! I\'m reaching out to see if you\'re ready to book your moving service with us. If you\'re all set, you can go ahead and complete your booking through the following link:</em></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><em>👉 </em></strong><a href="https://competitiverelocation.com/delivery-services/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(53, 76, 151);"><strong><em>https://competitiverelocation.com/delivery-services/</em></strong></a></p><p><em style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;</em></p><p><em style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Please make sure to upload photos of the items listed in your inventory. If you need any assistance with the booking process, feel free to reach out—I\'d be happy to help!</em></p><p><em style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;</em></p><p><em style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">We look forward to working with you.</em></p><p><em style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;</em></p><p><em style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Best regards,</em></p><p><br></p><p><em style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Sales Representative&nbsp;</em></p><p><br></p><p><em style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Moving and Delivery Specialist</em></p><p><em style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">848-359-8030</em></p><p><a href="https://info@competitiverelocation.com/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(53, 76, 151);"><em>Competitive Relocation Service&nbsp;</em></a></p><p><br></p>', 'REACHING BACK TO THE CUSTOMER:', '2025-05-03 06:06:24', '2025-05-03 06:06:24'),
	(22, 'CALL AND CONFIRM MOVE', 'CALL AND CONFIRM MOVE', '<p class="ql-align-center"><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">"Licensed &amp; Insured "We Move, You Smile"</strong></p><p class="ql-align-center"><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Licensed &amp; Insured - Local &amp; Long Distance Moving</strong></p><p class="ql-align-center"><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">USDOT #1877921 MC #677599</strong></p><p class="ql-align-center"><a href="http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001GVRKb8RRPJy7HAgZV-PmHGjKnyM2PKTevVdrxMhZqbPolLX3yEeIr2NjILCOV_qbA-AQYt0aTnH9iL7nS16oRxZ7TYVf4qqcXKnLKTaWrFrrFMYR7J-ZYHfWK8eWrJ5YmEph2RKMzdSC51Bw36ObMCT-v8mMN79ZylHESkezoDfIp0Bt1exnOrQp9N4yMv4v17mP4QAJ9DbBXo1Y0ea9fleo-6Ha-oD7pgldkyhBf8jY0BMJQiA_83c-NIFq1vt6ahkUKkMpumIwAPPcdR8jimZIUMdWojgR-et5wcP3xspW3a68XD_wJZxTG-1fPC3JyDRx67Pq6FVJEEnrVvNhtzwlEVKf8H1b&amp;c=&amp;ch=" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(17, 85, 204);"><strong>www.competitiverelocation.com</strong></a><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;</strong></p><p class="ql-align-center"><br></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Reply By Email With Any Questions </strong><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">1129914245</strong></p><p><br></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">Your Moving Details:&nbsp;</strong></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Name: Alyssa Lear&nbsp;</strong></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Moving Date: 04/16/2025&nbsp;</strong></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Size of Move: 7500&nbsp;</strong></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Moving From: havre de grace, MD&nbsp;</strong></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Moving To: havre de grace, MD&nbsp;</strong></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Referred By: Online Request </strong><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">&nbsp;</strong></p><p><br></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">Leave the Planning, Packing and Hauling to us.&nbsp;</strong></p><p><br></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Dear Alyssa Lear,</strong></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">We understand your MOVING and want to confirm the date!!&nbsp;</strong></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Please review some of our rates below and call us back to schedule!!</strong></p><p><br></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">1-877-385-2919</strong></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">Services Include:</strong></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Loading/ Unloading</strong></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Transportation Between Locations</strong></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Lite Disassembly &amp; Reassembly</strong></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Standard Insurance</strong></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Dollies, Tools &amp; Pads</strong></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">NO Hidden Fees</strong></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS</strong></p><p><br></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">Q: Do I need to empty my drawers?</strong></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">A: ALL drawers need to be emptied in wood cabinets. Small 2 drawer metal file cabinets can be left full; four drawer metal file cabinets need top two drawers emptied. Lateral file cabinets need to be completely emptied.</strong></p><p><br></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">Q: How can I prepare my appliances?</strong></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">A: The moving crew will wrap these items in moving pads to protect them on the truck. To prepare items such as your dishwasher and washing machine, make sure there emptied and dried. In addition, the movers are not plumbers or electricians – you are responsible to have your refrigerator, washer and chandeliers disconnected. Please Note: The movers are not licensed to disconnect any water or gas hook-ups.</strong></p><p><br></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">Q: Can the moving company dispose of excess trash?</strong></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">A: Yes, but there is a charge for items taken to the waste disposal location, including the labor and time involved in driving to and from the location as well as a fee imposed by the management of the waste disposal location.</strong></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p><p><br></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">Q: Should I tip my movers?</strong></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">A: As in any other service industry, you may wish to thank your moving crew by offering gratuity. There is no set amount for this, but we can suggest you tip based on the satisfaction with your crew; with the general guideline or $5-10 per man per hour. If you feel the crew went above and beyond, you may certainly increase the amount accordingly.</strong></p><p><br></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">Q: Can I ride on the truck on moving day?</strong></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">A: We cannot allow transport of customers for liability reasons</strong></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p class="ql-align-center"><a href="http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001GVRKb8RRPJy7HAgZV-PmHGjKnyM2PKTevVdrxMhZqbPolLX3yEeIr2NjILCOV_qbA-AQYt0aTnH9iL7nS16oRxZ7TYVf4qqcXKnLKTaWrFrrFMYR7J-ZYHfWK8eWrJ5YmEph2RKMzdSC51Bw36ObMCT-v8mMN79ZylHESkezoDfIp0Bt1exnOrQp9N4yMv4v17mP4QAJ9DbBXo1Y0ea9fleo-6Ha-oD7pgldkyhBf8jY0BMJQiA_83c-NIFq1vt6ahkUKkMpumIwAPPcdR8jimZIUMdWojgR-et5wcP3xspW3a68XD_wJZxTG-1fPC3JyDRx67Pq6FVJEEnrVvNhtzwlEVKf8H1b&amp;c=&amp;ch=" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(17, 85, 204);"><strong>www.competitiverelocation.com</strong></a><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;</strong></p><p class="ql-align-center"><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><em> &nbsp; Copyright © 2025 All rights reserved.</em></strong></p>', 'CALL AND CONFIRM MOVE', '2025-05-03 07:39:39', '2025-05-03 07:39:39'),
	(23, 'GET A MOVING QUOTES', 'GET A MOVING QUOTES', '<p class="ql-align-center"><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">1 848-359-8030</strong></p><p class="ql-align-center"><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><img src="https://lh7-rt.googleusercontent.com/docsz/AD_4nXf9_ZwawesJtOrgF_Ezfoj8c6JmpiFDhiig19c3wvawz1Jz0oU1GGOtUX-vDhGYAR098l2sVROCdONPHyqblnOELQB4BJyJO5fcxgQA_ib9DSf0YsliuLWLB-f03vEXNciTuamMBg?key=7WYJYDLTCP5c_UKLlQO5wHDm" height="150" width="593"></strong></p><p class="ql-align-center"><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Licensed &amp; Insured</strong></p><p class="ql-align-center"><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Family Owned Since 2008</strong></p><p class="ql-align-center"><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);">Local &amp; Long Distance Moving</strong></p><p class="ql-align-center"><a href="http://r20.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001GVRKb8RRPJy7HAgZV-PmHGjKnyM2PKTevVdrxMhZqbPolLX3yEeIr2NjILCOV_qbA-AQYt0aTnH9iL7nS16oRxZ7TYVf4qqcXKnLKTaWrFrrFMYR7J-ZYHfWK8eWrJ5YmEph2RKMzdSC51Bw36ObMCT-v8mMN79ZylHESkezoDfIp0Bt1exnOrQp9N4yMv4v17mP4QAJ9DbBXo1Y0ea9fleo-6Ha-oD7pgldkyhBf8jY0BMJQiA_83c-NIFq1vt6ahkUKkMpumIwAPPcdR8jimZIUMdWojgR-et5wcP3xspW3a68XD_wJZxTG-1fPC3JyDRx67Pq6FVJEEnrVvNhtzwlEVKf8H1b&amp;c=&amp;ch=" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(17, 85, 204);"><strong>www.competitiverelocation.com</strong></a><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;</strong></p><p class="ql-align-center"><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span class="ql-cursor">﻿</span></strong></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">ID:&nbsp;</strong></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Name:</strong></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Moving Date:&nbsp;</strong></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Size of Move:&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Moving From:&nbsp;</strong></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Moving To:&nbsp;</strong></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Referred By:</strong></p><p><br></p><p class="ql-align-center"><br></p><p><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Leave the Planning, Packing and Hauling to us. Your Local and Long Distance reading,PA Movers.</span></p><p><br></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"> Hi (Customer Name)!</strong></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">My name is Love, and I am reaching out to you in regards to your move. We need some information about your MOVE in order to provide an accurate quote.</strong></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">You can reply to this email, or call us today 9am-9pm&nbsp; 848-359-8030</strong></p><p><br></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(128, 128, 0);">We will need the following information:</strong></p><ul><li><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(12, 147, 242);">Size of your move-</strong><strong style="background-color: transparent;"> Is it an apartment, townhome, single family or commercial location that you need help moving?</strong></li><li><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(12, 147, 242);">Inventory List-</strong><strong style="background-color: transparent;"> We need to know an itemized list, it\'s best to go room by room and include everything to ensure that your estimate will be accurate.&nbsp;</strong></li><li><strong style="background-color: transparent;">What Floor are you on?</strong></li><li><strong style="background-color: transparent;">Do you have stairs?</strong></li><li><strong style="background-color: transparent;">Do you need storage?</strong></li><li><strong style="background-color: transparent;">What Date?&nbsp;</strong></li><li><strong style="background-color: transparent;">Are you packing?</strong></li><li><strong style="background-color: transparent;">Do you need boxes?&nbsp;</strong></li><li><strong style="background-color: transparent;">Do you need help packing?</strong></li><li><strong style="background-color: transparent;">What\'s your budget?</strong></li></ul><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp;</strong></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(40, 161, 214);">lamar reyes</strong></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><em>Moving Specialist</em></strong></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Competitive Relocation Services</strong></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Email: love@competitiverelocation.com</strong></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Phone: 848 359 8030</strong></p><p><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Website:</strong><a href="http://www.competitiverelocation.com" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><strong> </strong></a><a href="http://www.competitiverelocation.com" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(17, 85, 204);"><strong>www.competitiverelocation.com</strong></a><strong style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">&nbsp; </strong></p><p><strong style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">****** If you can not open the attachment, please email your inventory list to: love@competitiverelocation.com to get your</strong><a href="https://competitiverelocation.com/delivery-services/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;"><strong> </strong></a><a href="https://competitiverelocation.com/delivery-services/" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" style="color: rgb(17, 85, 204); background-color: transparent;"><strong>FREE QUOTE STARTED</strong></a></p><p><br></p>', 'GET A MOVING QUOTES', '2025-05-03 07:41:12', '2025-05-03 07:41:12'),
